{"tid":732399,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"高達 Gundam 真人版電影開拍　景甜飾演馬茜？！","createTime":"2018-07-07T01:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T17:29:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"06e821f8a59afabb8c7b84b1ed5251a8340e7d1c","tid":732399,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/GUNDAM_Bose_01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FGUNDAM_Bose_01.png&h=563d0e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《機動戰士高達》Gundam 推出至今已接近 40 年，成功吸引全球多國的支持者。如今， Sunrise 與傳奇影業（LEGENDARY Pictures）在 Anime Expo 2018中，正式宣布合作拍攝《機動戰士高達》真人版電影。<br />\n<br />\n在發布會中，他們僅宣布電影會由兩間公司共同製作，上映日期、演員及劇本等一切細節均未有定案。有評論認為，「元祖高達」 RX-78-2 於荷里活電影《挑戰者一號》中現身，令全球影迷十分興奮，導致傳奇影業下定決心將這套作品拍成真人版，拉上大銀幕。<br />\n<br />\n而傳奇影業亦曾製作過《蝙蝠俠》黑暗騎士三部曲、《戰狼三百》、《星際啟示錄》、《悍戰太平洋》等大作電影。當中《悍戰太平洋》更有大量機械人對戰的 CG 鏡頭，相信這些經驗對製作《高達》真人版十分有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n而值得一提的是，自 2016 年，傳奇影業被王健林創辦的萬達集團收購後，所製作的電影均會起用中國女演員景甜擔任女主角。這樣令不少高達迷都擔心，如電影以宇宙世紀（Universal Century）為背景，可能會看到景甜扮演馬茜或是娜娜這些經典女主角吧？<br />\n<br />\n事實上，早於 2000 年， Sunrise 曾與加拿大公司合作，拍攝一套名為《G-Saviour》的真人電影作品，但最後因為反應極度冷淡，整個系列最後不了了之，被 Sunrise 視作「黑歷史」作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/AqK6brL7-Et7xrIBubktRnll_UZb_2s8Lm2hFi5toRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FAqK6brL7-Et7xrIBubktRnll_UZb_2s8Lm2hFi5toRY.jpg&h=ba7aaa50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/2BvdbRv5RcTexFeR94o3KBRATDSuaJsLiwAXwosAF8I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F2BvdbRv5RcTexFeR94o3KBRATDSuaJsLiwAXwosAF8I.jpg&h=a3b7996a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲真人電影《G-Saviour》反應慘淡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/DHlw7LzyM-msfFpl_4tsuQwalF-UkWt8AEX3nwBF958.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FDHlw7LzyM-msfFpl_4tsuQwalF-UkWt8AEX3nwBF958.jpg&h=45ef26e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲PS1 遊戲《GUNDAM 0079：War For Earth》亦有真人扮演馬沙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/06/gundam-real-people-movie/movie-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2Fgundam-real-people-movie%2Fmovie-2%2F&d=3X0jM9FLq164Jbl1oY%2FURpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=3d2a8919\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/06/gundam-real-people-movie/movie-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90faf1a0f9b452f551de75ac0ca613a69d91154","tid":732399,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"同人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb794b4c6da8ba10bdcb1d59a17b7287523dd4e9","tid":732399,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:24:46.000Z","msg":"個種歷史感<br />\n戰爭感<br />\n希望唔好拍到垃圾咁"},{"pid":"9c5026e7a9457330cbd3f1b62e4a6521b1bd5a4e","tid":732399,"uid":98431,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:26:24.000Z","msg":"呢條女係咪軍雞黎 邊套都見到佢"},{"pid":"61f6bb0eaab906c5ce64e41a2952f687338c251c","tid":732399,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:27:18.000Z","msg":"拍08小隊ok?"},{"pid":"ea2fcac2e1de0f3d382051cb988e72e1ba4422ac","tid":732399,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"強国人點樣可以扮外國人呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d278c92fab3a30daa6d3468ea768c61bc6f2a183","tid":732399,"uid":60333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"景甜究竟憑咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055965b